## 📚 What I Learned

- Designing production-grade VPC architecture on AWS
- Implementing network segmentation with public/private subnets
- Configuring Auto Scaling with target tracking policies
- Setting up Application Load Balancer with health checks
- Securing infrastructure using layered security groups
- Using Bastion Host pattern for secure server access
- High availability design across multiple Availability Zones

